# Claude Code
# Ignore .claude/ by default, but track the team agent definitions — they're generic
# and worth versioning. Note: a bare `.claude/` would make the negations below
# unreachable (git won't descend into an excluded directory), hence `.claude/*`.
.claude/*
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/team-context.md

# Never track team data — guardian emails/phones for minors' families, consent records.
.claude/team-data/
CLAUDE.md

